'How ya doin’' Mr. Bledsoe said as he embraced Logan. He then picked up his son and they gave each other a huge hug.

The moment led to a standing ovation from the crowd as many fans shed tears at the emotional reunion. Mr. Bledsoe has been serving in Afghanistan for nine months.

'It’s been really hard, just to live by myself with my mom, grandma and grandpa,' Logan told KTVK.

