While his father has been serving abroad, Logan had chatted with his dad as often as possible through Skype.

Mr. Bledsoe said he was somewhat surprised at how emotional his son got after seeing him.

'I feel great,' Bledsoe said. 'I didn’t expect that much of a reaction from him ... It was more than I thought it would be.'

The reunion was made possible by the Phoenix Suns and the Streets of New York, a local pizza chain that sponsors the 'Welcome Home Hero' campaign.

